= 李昌(Chang Li)

~~~
{blanks}{img_left}{./figure/lc.JPG}{Li}{150px}{123x}{./figure/lc.jpg}
Cheers! I'm a final year PhD student at [http://ilps.science.uva.nl ILPS], [http://http://www.uva.nl/en/home University of Amsterdam, UvA], supervised by [https://staff.fnwi.uva.nl/m.derijke/ Prof. Dr. Maarten de Rijke]. 
I am interested in designing online algorithms that solve ranking problems. Typically, I focus on the following topics: online learning to rank, multi-armed bandits, federated learning. 
I received my bachelor degree from [http://www.tju.edu.cn/english/ TJU] in 2013. My mentor was [http://www.tjucs.win/faculty/wangxin/index-en.html Dr. Xin Wang]. 
Then I received my master degree from [http://en.ustc.edu.cn/ USTC], supervised by [http://staff.ustc.edu.cn/~hchen Prof. Dr. Huanhuan Chen] in 2016. 
You may find more about me in my [./ChangLi_CV.pdf CV].

